ERISA
 
(i) within ten days after a Responsible Officer learns that any "reportable event" (as defined in Section 4043(c) of ERISA), other than a reportable event for which the 30-day notice requirement has been waived by the PBGC, has occurred with respect to a Pension Plan, a statement setting forth details as to such reportable event and the action proposed to be taken with respect thereto;
 
