Waiver
 
9. . This Agreement shall be governed by the laws of the State of Minnesota, and the rights and obligations of the parties hereunder shall be construed, determined and enforced in accordance with the laws of the State of Minnesota, without regard to Minnesota common law or statutory choice-of-law principles. All disputes between the parties arising out of the interpretation, performance or breach of this Agreement shall be submitted for adjudication to a state or federal court located in the State of Minnesota.
Choice of Law; Jurisdiction; Venue
 
