ITEM 7.01    Regulation FD Disclosure
On November 13, 2006, Apogee Enterprises, Inc. issued a press release increasing its fiscal year 2007 earnings guidance to range of $0.92 to $0.98 per share. This is an update to the guidance communicated in its October 23, 2006 press release of $0.88 to $0.94 per share. A copy this press release is furnished as Exhibit 99.1 to this Current Report on Form 8-K, and is incorporated herein by reference.
ITEM 9.01    FINANCIAL STATEMENTS AND EXHIBITS
 
 
