ITEM 2.02 RESULTS OF OPERATIONS AND FINANCIAL CONDITION
On December 20, 2006, Apogee Enterprises, Inc. issued a press release announcing its financial results for the third quarter of fiscal 2007. A copy of this press release is furnished (not filed) as Exhibit 99.1 to this Current Report on Form 8-K, and is incorporated herein by reference.
ITEM 9.01 FINANCIAL STATEMENTS AND EXHIBITS
