Service of Process
5.4. . No Participant, surviving spouse, joint or contingent annuitant or beneficiary shall have the power to transmit, assign, alienate, dispose of, pledge or encumber any benefit payable under this Officers' SERP before its actual payment to such person. The Principal Sponsor shall not recognize any such effort to convey any interest under this Officers' SERP. No benefit payable under this Officers' SERP shall be subject to attachment, garnishment, execution following judgment or other legal process before actual payment to such person.
Spendthrift Provision
