On December 16, 2009, Apogee Enterprises, Inc. issued a press release announcing its financial results for the third quarter of fiscal 2010. A copy of this press release is furnished (not filed) as Exhibit 99.1 to this Current Report on Form 8-K, and is incorporated herein by reference.
 
