WHEREAS, Huffer has served as the Chief Executive Officer ("") of Apogee and a member of the Board of Directors of Apogee (the "") since January 1998, and the Chairman of the Board since June 1999;
CEO
Board
WHEREAS, Huffer has announced his intention voluntarily to retire from his officer positions with Apogee upon the election by the Board of Huffer's successor as CEO of Apogee;
WHEREAS, the Board wants to recognize Huffer's many years of loyal service to Apogee and to provide for the smooth transition of the CEO position;
WHEREAS, the parties desire to set forth all matters regarding Huffer's retirement as CEO; and
WHEREAS, the Board believes it is in the best interests of Apogee's shareholders to enter into this Agreement.
