I am very pleased with our fiscal 2013 results, as our earnings per share more than tripled to $0.66 on revenue growth of 6 percent in commercial construction markets that continued to be flat, said Joseph F. Puishys, Apogee chief executive officer. Our architectural backlog is up 25 percent from the
